Class ContactAutoSyncWorkItem

  • entity.ContactAutoSyncWorkItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bean, EventAware, KeyableBean, WorkItem

    public class ContactAutoSyncWorkItem
implements Bean, WorkItem, KeyableBean, EventAware
    Queue of Contact AddressBookUID to be auto synced. This is a system-internal entity.
